To view what's written in a file. --> cat filename
To change the access permissions of files. --> chmod 
To check which commands you have run till now. --> history
To remove a directory/ Folder. --> rmdir
To create a fruits.txt file and to view the content. --> vi fruits.txt , cat fruits.txt
Add content in devops.txt (One in each line) - Apple, Mango, Banana, Cherry, Kiwi, Orange, Guava. --> vi devops.txt and then press i and enter the content
To Show only top three fruits from the file. --> head -3 fruits.txt
To Show only bottom three fruits from the file. --> tail -3 fruits.txt
To create another file Colors.txt and to view the content. touch Colors.txt and then use cat command to view the content
Add content in Colors.txt (One in each line) - Red, Pink, White, Black, Blue, Orange, Purple, Grey. --> vi Colors.txt and add the content in insert mode.
To find the difference between fruits.txt and Colors.txt file. diff fruits.txt Colors.txt --> diff fruits.txt Colors.txt
